<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap');
        
        body {
            height: 100vh;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 4rem;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-family: "Space Mono", monospace;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3rem;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        button {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;

            background-color: #a91e50;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.2rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            color: white;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background-color: #b82d60;
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        p {
            font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="w-100">
        <div class="w-100" style="height: 60vh; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #d9e98c, #F2F6D0);">
            <div class="container h-100">
                <h1 class="text-center mb-2" style="color: #a91e50">MEAL SUGGESTOR</h1>
                <p class="description">Find your desired meals</p>
                <button class="mt-3">Get Started</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-100">
        <div class="w-100 h-auto pb-5" style="background-color: whitesmoke;">
            <div class="container h-100" style="justify-content: start;">
                <h2 class="mt-3" style="color: #5d704b;">How to use?</h2>
                <div class="container border rounded p-5 mt-3 mb-5 h-auto" style="justify-content: start; width: 680px; background-color: white;">
                    <h2 class="mb-4">MEAL SUGGESTOR MANUAL</h2>
                    <p class="text-center">Get quality meals with your provided ingredients</p>
                    <div class="w-100 ps-3 mb-3" style="border-left: 1px solid black;">
                        <p>Ingredients in search bar should have a comma between them. The resulted meals consist of name, thumbnail and its details ingredients, including missed ingredients.</p>
                        <p>A notification will appear if there are no meals that match the given ingredients.</p>
                    </div> 

                    <form class="form-inline w-50 m-auto mt-3">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon1">@</span>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="ingredients" placeholder="rice, egg" disabled>
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-success" disabled>Find</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <div class="container border rounded p-5 mt-3 h-auto" style="justify-content: start; width: 680px; background-color: white;">
                    <h2 class="mb-4">NEED CONSULTATION?</h2>
                    <p class="text-center">Nutritionists are always ready to help.</p>
                    <div class="w-100 ps-3 mb-3" style="border-left: 1px solid black;">
                        <p>Qualified nutritionists can be hired to improve your current diet. Make your dream goal closure with personalized advices and meal plans.</p>
                        <p>Nutritionists undergo, including testing and interviews before becoming official consultants. This ensures that the delivered programs are professional, effective, and achievable.</p>
                    </div> 

                    <button class="mt-3" style="background-color: #889E73;">Hire Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="w-100 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="height: 4rem; background-color: #C1CFA1;">
        Â© 2024 Meal Suggestor
    </footer>
</body>
</html>